{"tid":880671,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[上進心］生活無憂之後冇上進心有冇問題？","createTime":"2018-10-29T01:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T07:04:00.000Z","uid":141869,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"13fc1708536109471c4b780ed33b19ef797442b3","tid":880671,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T01:21:22.000Z","msg":"講返背景先，<br />\n27歲搵緊接近三萬，<br />\n上年靠屋企人幫手買左樓，<br />\n月供完再比返啲屋企每月剩返一萬鬆啲洗，<br />\n唔煙唔酒唔賭錢唔課金，<br />\n得閒都係搵fd做運動食飯打下機咁，<br />\n隨緣升職，<br />\n突然覺得好似都冇乜野要煩，<br />\n又冇晒當初入職ge個團火，<br />\n是是旦旦返工又一日，<br />\n咩都唔洗理長期咁生活好似都唔錯，<br />\n大家覺得有冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：冇女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46babd41b7c02d3cbe040639b3cf5dce86ef554e","tid":880671,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T01:34:20.000Z","msg":"負皮上一頁"},{"pid":"d73bf280363f4eb080539443c772c0b78e667b13","tid":880671,"uid":79632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T01:37:11.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過冇樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee66655e726d038de5d29fb8a0ba46ecf7b5064a","tid":880671,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46babd41b7c02d3cbe040639b3cf5dce86ef554e","tid":880671,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T01:34:20.000Z","msg":"負皮上一頁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T01:38:21.000Z","msg":"點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f3036f749af1a6040d8e4cd27e9f40f8dfaf21","tid":880671,"uid":104668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T01:43:01.000Z","msg":"無女係重點"},{"pid":"fdd772d7c3fb13dae4dc1f5281ec9b4326d4e36e","tid":880671,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T07:04:00.000Z","msg":"推<